    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行不应因通胀下滑而放松警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/lagarde-says-ecb-shouldn-t-lower-its-guard-as-inflation-tumbles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德 (Christine Lagarde) 表示，政策制定者绝不能因近期通胀率跌至 2% 而沾沾自喜。这表明投资者押注即将降息可能为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/lagarde-says-ecb-shouldn-t-lower-its-guard-as-inflation-tumbles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 14:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
